zerowallcli (1.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Added support for Firewall Zones (--zone, --get-zones, etc.).
  * Implemented Rule Persistence (--permanent, --reload).
  * Standardized CLI help and documentation formatting.
  * Added specialized listing commands (--list-all, --list-ports, --list-services).
  * Improved iptables controller with custom chain and save/restore support.

 -- ZeroWall Team <support@zerowall.io>  Sun, 15 Mar 2026 10:15:00 +0600

